{"tid":1417804,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急】 組織番多次二百萬人上街 就可以對準目標 清晰訴求","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:28:32.000Z","uid":275507,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"94d9eda059d445d26c86040c2893289c98a629b5","tid":1417804,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"六月十六日，香港人締造歷史，二百萬零一人上街。 <br />\n<br />\n係過去果兩個月，我地清楚見到政府無顧訴求既反應，警犬濫用私刑發癲發狂，中聯辦黑社會既惡行，過百烈士被捕，無理被控暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">作為抗爭左兩個月既香港市民，我地需要更進一步對準政權！將呢兩個月既怒氣重新集氣！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可以再比政府轉移視線！重新我地不分化，不割席既立場！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盡快選好時機，係二百萬人上街兩個月後，再一次統一戰線，對準政權</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">8月17，18 係好日子，可以準備充足文宣，將過去兩個月發生既事回顧，同時都要定下目標死線，如果政府依然無回應，<span style=\"color: red;\">我地就有充份理據升級，到時風向可以完全歸邊</span></span>"},{"pid":"799ee029ef098d2c1819d625affc86c0759f54a6","tid":1417804,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645fff17329401f30471e197bbc87f598877f143","tid":1417804,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d7a2e97aedfa2e35e723d64dfb60c9f6401850","tid":1417804,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef645dee879c3f6479421171c0446201bf697d2","tid":1417804,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62891e118eae0efc15c3f1ab579adb4f2f4a776b","tid":1417804,"uid":275507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor